OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775146264
OL,3,CMotorists warned to expect major
OL,4,Cdelays after car crash on M23 near
OL,5,CGatwick
OL,7,FMotorists are being warned of major
OL,8,Fdelays after a car crash on the M23 in
OL,9,FWest Sussex.
OL,11,FThe incident happened shortly after
OL,12,F5am on Thursday morning, after a car
OL,13,Ftravelling northbound collided with
OL,14,Fthe central reservation and a tree
OL,15,Fbetween junctions nine, near Gatwick
OL,16,FAirport, and 10, in Crawley.
OL,18,FIt comes as millions of drivers are
OL,19,Fexpected to embark on getaway trips
OL,20,Fahead of the Easter bank holiday
OL,21,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
