CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775146264
OL,3,CMotorists warned to expect major
OL,4,Cdelays after car crash on M23 near
OL,5,CGatwick
OL,7,FNational Highways South East said
OL,8,Fmotorists could expect delays of
OL,9,Faround 70 minutes on top of their
OL,10,Fnormal journey time, in an update
OL,11,Fpublished at 9am.
OL,13,FSussex Police said it is investigating
OL,14,Fthe crash, which injured three people
OL,15,F- two men and a woman.
OL,17,FThe force warned that the northbound
OL,18,Fcarrigeway will be closed for a
OL,19,F"number of hours" while it
OL,20,Finvestigates.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
